訓低之後都有一格六月講梟既力量細左，所以隻野都九成神父控制<br />\n所以之後就有神父痴漢分身之術摸亞門既畫面出現左<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f31b0228b2b618af7001e16e13d6f65fa428c4e2","tid":631560,"uid":36820,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T17:19:43.000Z","msg":"唄睇黎會被口盾搞掂"},{"pid":"23aeacd2e5e38ca2beaab705694d18e9eed5f892","tid":631560,"uid":128089,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T17:27:33.000Z","msg":"呢個先係討論PO，咪再推D垃圾PO上嚟，<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/631573/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/631573/page/1</a>"}]}